      public Movie(MovieType type, String title, MovieStatus status, String synopsis, String director, String[] cast, MovieRating movieRating, List<Review> pastReviews, double ticketSales)
      Creates a Movie with the given parameters Overall rating is generated and updated independently based on pastReviews
      Parameters:
      type - Movie type
      title - Movie title
      status - Movie showing status
      synopsis - Movie synopsis
      director - Director of the movie
      cast - Cast involved in the movie
      movieRating - Movie audience rating
      pastReviews - Reviews about the movie
      ticketSales - Sales generated from selling tickets for this movie
